Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有珍奇的东西流到这海滩上来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方的水实和贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}水实:一种盆装的供品。将生的黄瓜,茄子,\N豇豆这类东西细细切碎制成。类似的还有水子,水米,水物。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的深海鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会很少有地出现人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是没人乘的空船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:21.55,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1000)}{\pos(0,0)}{\1c&H643B3B\1a&H00}{\p1} m 95 38 l 180 38 180 480 95 480 {\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:21.55,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1000)}{\pos(112,64)}来\N自\N海\N境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1000)}{\an8\pos(78,70)}{\fs18\shad0\bord1.5\alpha&H80\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}海\N境\N:\N分\N隔\N海\N神\N国\N和\N人\N类\N国\N的\N分\N界\N线\N。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到对面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说从这里有到海湾另一边的渡船出海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间大家不都在打渔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那等到白天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这海面上与妻子以奇怪的方式分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你不想听这种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讲一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是两年或者再往前半年的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是鱼腥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你出生在这么乡下的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦 回哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 求求父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯了那种错误就要被赶走 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来说我导致店里生意下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了解雇我而找的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 为什么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲明明说了让你继承我家家业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为与你的婚约而导致同辈嫉妒得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是被他们灌了不少谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没想到会要跟我来这么偏僻的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我也没指望让你跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是长女 本来就还有打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去的话就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是适合你的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜绯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上岸后向她道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出霭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}霭:轻雾。气象学上将一千米内可见物称蔼,不可见称雾。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 还能清楚看见陆地 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就出海了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃船到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜绯 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 有蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是指哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜绯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜绯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船就那样翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我漂到了这个海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没找到妻子所乘的船的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个海滩 是因为潮水流向的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海面上的东西都一起被冲上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子乘的船也翻了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面装的货物至少也应该会被冲到这里一两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那样漂到海上丢了性命了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管哪个只要无法证实 我都无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你两年半都一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真难得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有没有证据都已经“不再活着”了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算万一得救的话 也已经展开了别的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也开始考虑下自己的事比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 我也有点多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 跟往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢每次关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 要把那个带到镇上卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种价钱 虽然我不了解镇上的行情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎样你也赚得太狠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再多要一倍也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你装什么明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可做了很久的批发商
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有你这种中间商
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的渔民才会这么穷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算加上从镇上到这里的劳力也就这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去这前面的村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里不能再让步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次开始就按这个数拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能拿这么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也跟大家说一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我总以为你是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天中间商也付了好价钱买我们的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 不成敬意 请拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你也离开现在住的地方到我们家的房子来住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里住下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不错哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天是大潮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么呢 潮水高得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在这里的 等妻子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人已经
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在村子里好好生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不管你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再来问我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不该哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感到很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间 你总说些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮水也不断上涨 总也不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也还是偶尔会一直往海面的方向看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像会轻易给海水冲走一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里也不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮水涨成这样 跟那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候也出了这种霭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 在它退下去之前还是别出海捕鱼比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一进到这种霭里 就会有回不来的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 听说差不多三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只剩下空船回来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有浪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算能回来 但是到海滩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意刚才听到的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来从那以后做了不少调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此也知道那个时机再次出现了 所以回来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的“蛇群”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人看不见是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西恐怕是“虫”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说过“海千山千”这句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}海千山千:来源跟银古说的一样,形容精通世事,老奸巨滑的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说在海里活千年 山里活千年的蛇会变成龟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西也有跟它相通之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也无法得知它们活了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是在像霭那样的东西产生的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成群到外海巡游的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与深山里悄悄生存的生物不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个外形都是一眼看去 与蛇无异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机来临 山里的下山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海里的往近海去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海面合流 千日后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回近海 变成一体的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时的蛇群一样的东西回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要到海里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那霭从外面什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很奇妙地 从里面看外面却看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想过为什么那时候只有你妻子被霭吞进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那霭里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有想返回陆地的人才看得到陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而回得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正因为发现了妻子的遗物而丧失了生存的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有了这些觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去长长见识也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在霭里看陆地清楚得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量真多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还有遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜绯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经开始放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你太慢了 都过去几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过去三天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样来救我 我抱怨太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不是真想抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点看看你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在 能看见陆地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 在对面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是涨潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该回的陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫开始变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再呆在这里就遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点离开那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 来高浪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 霭退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们漂流到海滩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人都没指望我们还活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只打算出海两 三个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是陆地上已经过了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个霭里是按虫的时间流逝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少这救了里面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的“三天”只在寂寞的记忆中就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人妻子的船漂到了海滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 上等的和服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已经
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍贵的果实
